1. Alternative 1 is type of resolution suggested by Jebb and reported in USUN’s 115, of July 10[19]:Telegram 115, July 19, not printed;
                        the thrust of Mr. Jebb’s earlier resolution is set forth in Delga 615, December 11, from Paris, p. 1302. See also telegram 59, July 10, from New
